   "width": 501.59999999999997,
   "height": 41.25,
   "text": "WINDOW VERIFIERS\nSolvencyVerifierAdapter · DepthPoCDArrayVerifier (chunked: 17.9KB < EIP-170,\ndeploys inline) · MockVerifier when USE_REAL_VERIFIERS≠1",
   "originalText": "WINDOW VERIFIERS\nSolvencyVerifierAdapter · DepthPoCDArrayVerifier (chunked: 17.9KB < EIP-170,\ndeploys inline) · MockVerifier when USE_REAL_VERIFIERS≠1",
