   "id": "z_pocd_t",
   "type": "text",
   "x": 1350,
   "y": 1382,
   "width": 349.8,
   "height": 68.75,
   "text": "depth_pocd_array.circom  (N=10 × 4 chunks)\n102 public signals per chunk (4 proofs cover 37\nticks; last chunk identity-padded) — order MUST match\nMONIAOracle._buildChunkSignals; proves published\ndepth curve = true decryption of accumulators",
   "originalText": "depth_pocd_array.circom  (N=10 × 4 chunks)\n102 public signals per chunk (4 proofs cover 37\nticks; last chunk identity-padded) — order MUST match\nMONIAOracle._buildChunkSignals; proves published\ndepth curve = true decryption of accumulators",
