   "height": 68.75,
   "text": "run_demo.sh (scripted)\nfresh vanilla Anvil → deploy_local.sh →\nregister_all.mjs → indexer + control →\nscenario.mjs: epoch 1 borrow→print→repay, epoch 2\nborrow→default→seize (REAL proofs)",
