   "width": 336.59999999999997,
   "height": 68.75,
   "text": "run_autonomous.sh (local) · run_fuji.sh (FUJI LIVE)\nALL SIX services, no script. Local: Anvil\n--block-time 1. Fuji: real chain, EPOCH_LEN=120 ·\nTENOR_BLOCKS=60 · KEEPER_STALL_S=300; fund_fuji.mjs\ngas-funds 8 actors from WALLET_PRIVATE_KEY",
